There's no body parsing middleware. If POST/PUT routes are added without size limits, the app becomes vulnerable to payload-based DoS attacks.

```js
app.use(express.json({ limit: '10kb' }));
app.use(express.urlencoded({ extended: true, limit: '10kb' }));
```

#### 3. No Rate Limiting
All endpoints are open to brute-force and flooding attacks.

